Egyptian mediation efforts will dispel tensions between Ankara and
Damascus, Egypt's Middle East News Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
Following a meeting with Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak here
on how to defuse the present Syria-Turkey crisis, al-Sharaa
