between Syria and Turkey," he added.
</P>
<P>
Al-Sharaa arrived here earlier in the day and left after the
meeting with Mubarak.
</P>
<P>
Mubarak visited Turkey and Syria Tuesday in his bid to contain
the escalating tensions between the two neighbors from developing
into armed conflicts. He has offered the two countries a set of
proposals to start a direct dialog for an immediate solution.
</P>
<P>
Strained ties between Syria and Turkey deteriorated in recent
weeks with Syria bridling at Turkey's growing military links with
Israel and Turkey threatening Damascus for allegedly aiding
Kurdish rebels fighting for autonomy in southeast Turkey. 
