<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange
index closed at 2,097.2 points Saturday, down 5.7 points
compared with that of Wednesday's closing.
</P>
<P>
The turnover plunged to 6.15 million Kuwaiti dinars (20.29
million U.S. dollars) from Wednesday's 12.14 million Kuwaiti
dinars (40.06 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of only 25.35 million shares were changed hands
in 691 deals Saturday as against 56.07 million shares in
1,246 deals Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The stock exchange was closed on Thursday and Friday.
</P>
</TEXT>
