Minister at the State House, said the Zambian government was
overwhelmed with the work PUSH was doing in addressing the plight
of the poor people.
</P>
<P>
He called on vulnerable people in Zambia to support and
utilize the chance which was aimed at equipping them with skills
in business entrepreneurship, sanitary activities as well as
bricklaying and block making.  
